LogFile.FinalText: It's unbelievable how much they look the same. This is what many think of the two Danish princesses. There are many similarities between Mary and Marie, but there are just as many - perhaps even more - differences. They are both foreigners, commoners, and have each found their prince of Denmark - Mary is married to Crown Prince Frederik and Marie to Prince Joachim. Even their names and looks remind extremely much about each other. Both have the look of models with long, dark hair and big, brown eyes. But in spite of the many similiarities, Mary and Marie are also independent women who have lived and live each their ways, which has had an impact on their values and personalities.
